Package cs351.utility

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Job
    A job can be added to any job list and submitted to a job system's worker threads for execution.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JobList
    Note :: This class is not safe to be used by multiple threads at once.
    ParallelJobGroup
    Note :: This is only to be used by the job system - see the JobList class which should be used to manage individual lists before submitting them to the job system.
    ParallelJobSystem
    A ParallelJobSystem provides an easy way to manage up to 256 threads.
    Vector2f
    Vector2f can maintain double values for x/y components and perform some vector operations with them.
    Vector4f
    A Vector4f can maintain double values for x/y/z components and perform vector operations on them.
    WorkerThread
    This is the WorkerThread class used by the job system.
